FinCal 0.1
================================================================
Released 2013-July-16

First official release of the FinCal R package.
Financial calculator for time value money.
Tools for computational finance.

Methods:
* pv.simple
* fv.simple
* pv.annuity
* fv.annuity
* pv.perpetuity
* pv
* fv
* fv.uneven
* pv.uneven
* pmt
* n.period
* r.continuous
* r.norminal
* ear
* ear.continuous
